# tour-3d: open the 3D layer-stack view on the SKY130 cell and orbit the camera so
# the extruded metal layers read in depth. The orbit is applied per captured frame,
# so the whole clip is a smooth turn around the stack.
viewport 1600x1000
use-case inspect-cell
settle
view3d on
wait 8
orbit 4 0
capture 90 20
